com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.util.transformers
Class AbstractTermTransformer

java.lang.Object
  com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.util.transformers.AbstractTermTransformer
All Implemented Interfaces:
ITermTransformer
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConjunctionNormalFormTransformer, EliminateConjunctionsTransformer, NegationNormalFormTransformer, NormalizeArithmeticComparatorsTransformer, NormalizeArrayTermsTransformer, OrderOperandsTransformer, RemoveAxiomaticExpressionsTransformer, RemoveDisjunctionsTransformer, RemoveIfThenElseTransformer, RemoveImplicationsTransformer, RemoveObserverFunctionsTransformer, RemoveSortDependingFunctionsTransformer, SimplifyConjunctionTransformer, SimplifyDisjunctionTransformer, SimplifyPostconditionTransformer, TermSimplificationTransformer
public abstract class AbstractTermTransformer
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITermTransformer

This class provides a lightweight framework for implementing Term parsers intended to transform Terms.

This class does NOT currently contain functionality to transform all forms of Terms, since it is primarily meant to be used by KeYTestGen, which only uses a subset of such terms. As need dictates, this may change to support all sorts of Term trees.

Author:
christopher
